name: Milk

name: Yogurt
comment: Using the powder milk DIAAS as a approximation. Milk and yogurt contain both 80% casein, 20% whey, however the lactic fermentation could transform the proteins - for the better or the worse. (yogurt is cooked then fermented milk)
